。」意指意大利已被大量中國遊客入侵，令他感覺身處在亞洲國家，反映了外國人歧視華人的問題，更辣㷫不少內地網民。<br />\n<br />\n適逢十一黃金周，不少內地人出外旅遊。在布魯克林的照片中，相中亞洲人並無任何不雅行為，反而只是普通的遊客在觀光，就被布魯克林指意大利到處都是華人，令這裡變得不像意大利，於是一眾網民斥布魯克林是歧視並侮辱了華人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.43pTJOtBqsbNfCgQ1xDLA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDYx/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/931dcc71658b4f5464051009ab1c3820\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.43pTJOtBqsbNfCgQ1xDLA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDYx%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F931dcc71658b4f5464051009ab1c3820&h=1becb0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碧咸未有在兒子的旅行相片現身，但他的Instagram都有大批網民留言，中英文雙管齊下，痛罵碧咸不懂得教兒子，要他們為辱華而道歉，甚至拒絕他們再來亞洲賺錢做生意等。而碧咸嫂Victoria日前亦身處巴黎出席朱古力品牌Pierre Marcolini活動，但她的ig一樣慘遭圍攻，不少網民大罵Victoria是「八婆」，以她們一家為恥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LP_ZUuf0LJ7Rmq8picaq0w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDY0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ff2706823ca0cf06f5629cf19d19d9d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLP_ZUuf0LJ7Rmq8picaq0w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9NDY0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fff2706823ca0cf06f5629cf19d19d9d1&h=5a25ae24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講事實,小小支那賤種狗玻璃心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4393ed367c5d680bd44f69e5842e52d41f7d58cd","tid":850078,"uid":34701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"玻璃心就玻璃心 也別勉強的慰問"},{"pid":"7cad8b90d38d668aa95c8771a7cad2b69c2ce31f","tid":850078,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"以經唔可以用「玻璃」